OL,3,CCamilla and Zara bring the glamour as
OL,4,CLadies Day returns to Cheltenham
OL,6,FThe return of Ladies Day to the
OL,7,FCheltenham Festival brought a touch of
OL,8,Fglamour to the racecourse with Zara
OL,9,FTindall and Carole Middleton spotted
OL,10,Flaughing as they walked arm in arm.
OL,12,FDubbed the greatest day on turf, the
OL,13,Fevent also welcomed the Queen, who
OL,14,Fcelebrated outstanding female sporting
OL,15,Ftalent by meeting a group of
OL,16,Ftrailblazing women.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
