OL,3,CCamilla and Zara bring the glamour as
OL,4,CLadies Day returns to Cheltenham
OL,6,FFashion was to the fore on Ladies Day
OL,7,F` held for the first time since 2019 `
OL,8,Fwith Camilla wearing a stylish Philip
OL,9,FTreacy hat featuring feathers and a
OL,10,Fcoat by Anna Valentine.
OL,12,FThe Princess Royal and Camilla's
OL,13,Fformer husband Andrew Parker-Bowles
OL,14,Fwere among the racegoers, and Mrs
OL,15,FMiddleton, the Princess of Wales's
OL,16,Fmother, posed for a picture with Mike
OL,17,Fand Zara Tindall and TV actor James
OL,18,FNesbitt.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
