OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773407484
OL,3,CCamilla and Zara bring the glamour as
OL,4,CLadies Day returns to Cheltenham
OL,6,FGuests invited to the royal box
OL,7,Fincluded the Queen's son Tom Parker
OL,8,FBowles, daughter Laura Lopes and her
OL,9,Fhusband Harry.
OL,11,FCamilla, joint patron of the Jockey
OL,12,FClub, is a regular at the biggest
OL,13,Foccasion in the jump racing calendar
OL,14,Fand walked through the grounds past
OL,15,Fpunters holding up camera phones to
OL,16,Fmeet the sporting women in the parade
OL,17,Fring.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
