OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773407484
OL,3,CCamilla and Zara bring the glamour as
OL,4,CLadies Day returns to Cheltenham
OL,6,FShe briefly caught up with Mrs
OL,7,FTindall, who said: "How are you, good
OL,8,Fto see you". The Queen replied: "Very
OL,9,Fwell."
OL,11,FThe Queen chatted to Natasha Hunt and
OL,12,FZoe Aldcroft, two members of England's
OL,13,FWomen's Rugby World Cup winning side,
OL,14,Fand Rachael Blackmore, the first
OL,15,Ffemale jockey to win both the Grand
OL,16,FNational and the Cheltenham Gold Cup.
